00:37:51.150 --> 00:37:56.970
There's a new idea coming up
now, after this recent crisis,

00:37:56.970 --> 00:38:03.180
and it's called CoVaR.

00:38:03.180 --> 00:38:09.470
And this is a concept emphasized
by Professor

00:38:09.470 --> 00:38:15.280
